verbose_text: Although we did not find a significant correlation between the expression of HIF-1alpha and HIF-2alpha with gender, age, calcification, or Hashimoto 's disease in the present study (P> 0.05), both of their expressions were correlated to lymph node metastasis (P < 0.05), capsular invasion (P < 0.05), and TNM stage (P < 0.05).
